{"tid":979799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼拒以否決預算案施壓","createTime":"2019-01-13T04:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T07:36:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b300cbd59a929ccdc8ccc8faf45c627e5a343d94","tid":979799,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:17:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190113/20589836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190113%2F20589836&d=0H4oW%2BgquIP99nIvOe5VJZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=9ef14d95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190113%2F20589836&h=cef2cf23\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190113/20589836</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月13日 <br />\n<br />\n李慧琼拒以否決預算案施壓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190113/large/13la3p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190113%2Flarge%2F13la3p4.jpg&h=47cf39f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李慧琼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府擬由下月起調高領取長者綜援合資格年齡，政策本來已激起反對，後因特首林鄭月娥卸責給議員再引發軒然大波。民主派日前邀請建制派合作，以否決財政預算案為籌碼逼港府撤回政策。獲林鄭致電「耍冧」的民建聯李慧琼昨即拒絕民主派邀請，並批評民主派的建議過於草率及不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：團體抗議　高呼「林鄭！撤！」<br />\n<br />\n反斥民主派草率<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼昨日出席電台節目時指，民建聯已約見財政司司長陳茂波，要求當局修改政策，又表明不因為單一政策而否決預算案，她指「我哋連財政預算案有乜嘢內容都未掌握，你就叫我哋去承諾或者考慮去否決財政預算案&hellip;&hellip;我認為係太過草率，同埋唔係好負責任嘅一個選擇」，故此不接受這種處理方法。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨黨魁楊岳橋則認為，今次事件關乎林鄭的政治涵養問題，又指只要向政府施加足夠的壓力，就能迫使當局擱置政策，「如果壓力係夠嘅話，我相信政府係願意更改嘅」。民主黨黃碧雲亦表示，長者如非貧窮都不會申領綜援，當局不應如此刻薄，她續說，若政策得不到跨黨派和市民支持，出台後都會遇到強烈反彈，冀建制派合力要求政府撥亂反正。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n收緊長者綜援全城震怒　政府補鑊擬放寬60-64歲就業規定<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n團體抗議　高呼「林鄭！撤！」<br />\n<br />\n團體抗議　高呼「林鄭！撤！」<br />\n失推翻時機　社福界兩手準備<br />\n收緊長者綜援全城震怒政府補鑊　擬放寬60-64歲就業規定"},{"pid":"506b1665eedcb6a4de95957d6dfde113638f841b","tid":979799,"uid":228963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:20:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd1031b55a80d3b8f45d9027503a2d944acb9986","tid":979799,"uid":52006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:21:19.000Z","msg":"出賣你地班廢老幾多次你地咪又投番比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959efa43cdaee447abc509d03e31c4ab4e4bb730","tid":979799,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"請廣傳俾廢老"},{"pid":"41d44aa317d27ee8153811ad410e0f890d1084b3","tid":979799,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"奸到出哂面呢d人渣幾時死啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9ef0a9cbcea0a53bcdc9f6021dbe825b23d8ef","tid":979799,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"全城<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢老</span></span></strong>震怒"},{"pid":"52a282972a3502e24f89e0fec22ae33561ad6833","tid":979799,"uid":35021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCXXVk6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCXXVk6.jpg&h=bc35837c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afcc4b8141d26c481b1bf03309eebdea8304d36b","tid":979799,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"我地民建聯都嬲,但都唔可以否決預算案咁激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff55d059313e197f8350ba7b5cb405dae1ed0261","tid":979799,"uid":153689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:38:00.000Z","msg":"笑撚死，講到幾反對，要你否決政府又拒絕<br />\n做狗做到出晒面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk